      <title>随着旅游业的复苏，菲律宾航空设定了 4.5 亿美元的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/philippine-air-sets-450-million-of-spending-as-tourism-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾航空公司已为今年的支出预算设定为 4.5 亿美元，是 2023 年分配的 1.7 亿美元的两倍多，为旅游业的持续复苏和更激烈的竞争做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/philippine-air-sets-450-million-of-spending-as-tourism-rebounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 09:33:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
