      <title>卢比处于四年低点引发干预和加息讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/rupiah-dips-to-four-year-low-on-bond-outflows-dollar-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元全面反弹和债券大量外流，卢比跌至四年低点，印尼央行对货币市场进行了干预，以稳定卢比汇率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/rupiah-dips-to-four-year-low-on-bond-outflows-dollar-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 02:11:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧佩克减产和地缘政治风险推动油价上涨至 85 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国原油期货自 10 月份以来首次突破 85 美元，这是在 OPEC+ 减产、需求强劲和地缘政治风险加剧的背景下上涨的最新里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
